#doitforyou : Let Your Vision Lead Your Dream

One trick for the law of attraction is to allow your vision for your life to be the light that will guide your steps in darkness.

🌻The only person who can create a vision (a path leading your dream ) is YOU, and this vision can be anything that you desire. 

🔗So put a vision board ( a poster or in collage format ) in your room, set a motivational wallpaper on your laptop and cell phone background, put a picture of your goal on your fridge and wardrobe, and make sure that you remember the feeling the attainment of your goal.

▪️Every time you look at these pictures, that feeling will get reinforced and strengthened which in turn will make your vibration a powerful magnetic force for your dream!

Make your dream a reality💫💫 !!! 

Happy Monday !!!! With @davidoffcafe

#lifeupdate // Sharing a personal win that may be small to some, but means the world to me.👇🥰 #WellnessCoach #certified 

For the longest time, I’ve known — deep in my gut — that ‘ Wellness ‘ is far more significant, wholesome, and complex than what it appears on the surface. It’s not just about food or fitness… it’s a way of being. 🌿

I’ve always trusted that true wellness intertwines the body, mind, and spirit — and that spirituality and mindset are inseparable threads in this tapestry of self growth.

✨ And today, I’m finally living a wish I’ve carried for years — to understand wellness not just intuitively, but through a structured, studied, and process-oriented approach .

✌️I’m now a Certified Wellness Coach — a journey I undertook purely for my own growth and to ensure that everything I share comes from a space of integrity, lived experience, and knowledge.

❤️A heartfelt thank you to each one of you who has loved, supported, and resonated with my thoughts and experiences.

My life has always been my content —  shared with honesty. And when you tell me it helps you in even the smallest way, I feel deeply blessed. 🙏🏻

As a #WellnessCoach, I hope the knowledge I’ve gained adds even more value to those who have always believed in me and in SHVTAS . 

Here’s to growing, healing, and evolving — together. 🌿✨
